OL,3,CSupreme Court to rule on motor finance
OL,4,Ccompensation row
OL,6,FThe Supreme Court is to rule on Friday
OL,7,Fon whether millions of motorists could
OL,8,Fbe entitled to compensation on their
OL,9,Fhire-purchase agreements.
OL,11,FIn October last year, the Court of
OL,12,FAppeal ruled that "secret" commission
OL,13,Fpayments to car dealers as part of
OL,14,Ffinance arrangements made before 2021
OL,15,Fwithout the motorist's fully informed
OL,16,Fconsent were unlawful.
