OL,6,FThe Financial Conduct Authority (FCA)
OL,7,Fhas also intervened in the case,
OL,8,Ftelling the UK's highest court that
OL,9,Fthe Court of Appeal ruling "goes too
OL,10,Ffar", while the three motorists oppose
OL,11,Fthe challenge.
OL,13,FLords Reed, Hodge, Lloyd-Jones, Briggs
OL,14,Fand Hamblen are due to hand down their
OL,15,Fruling at 4.35pm on Friday.
