OL,3,CSupreme Court to rule on motor finance
OL,4,Ccompensation row
OL,6,FThe outcome of the ruling could have
OL,7,Fmajor consequences for the industry,
OL,8,Fwith the FCA telling the Supreme Court
OL,9,Flast year that almost 99% of the
OL,10,Froughly 32 million car finance
OL,11,Fagreements entered into since 2007
OL,12,Finvolved a commission payment to a
OL,13,Fbroker.
OL,15,FThe three drivers, Marcus Johnson,
OL,16,FAndrew Wrench and Amy Hopcraft, all
OL,17,Fused car dealers as brokers for
OL,18,Ffinance arrangements for second-hand
OL,19,Fcars, all worth less than #10,000.
