OL,3,CSupreme Court to rule on motor finance
OL,4,Ccompensation row
OL,6,FOnly one finance option was presented
OL,7,Fto the motorists in each case, with
OL,8,Fthe car dealers making a profit from
OL,9,Fthe sale of the car and receiving
OL,10,Fcommission from the lender.
OL,12,FThe commission paid to dealers was
OL,13,Faffected by the interest rate on the
OL,14,Floan.
OL,16,FThe schemes were banned by the FCA in
OL,17,F2021, with the three drivers taking
OL,18,Flegal action individually between 2022
OL,19,Fand 2023.
