OL,6,FIf they side with the lenders, then it
OL,7,Fis likely to significantly limit the
OL,8,Fscope of potential payouts to
OL,9,Fmotorists.
OL,11,FThe FCA has said it will confirm
OL,12,Fwithin six weeks of the judgment
OL,13,Fwhether it is planning to launch a
OL,14,Fredress scheme.
